<td data-valign="top"><p>AN ainm an Tighearn Iosa,<br />
Agus Spiorad ìocshlain aigh,<br />
An ainm Athar Israil,<br />
    Sinim sios gu tamh.</p>
<p>Ma tha musal na dusal,<br />
Na run air bith dhomh ’n dan,<br />
Dhia fuasgail orm is cuartaich orm,<br />
    Is fuadaich uam mo namh.</p>
<p>An ainm Athar priseil,<br />
Is Spiorad iocshlain aigh,<br />
An ainm Tighearn Iosa,<br />
    Sinim sios gu tamh.<br />
*         *         *         *<br />
Dhia, cobhair mi is cuartaich mi,<br />
    O ’n uair ’s gu uair mo bhais.</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>IN name of the Lord Jesus,<br />
And of the Spirit of healing balm,<br />
In name of the Father of Israel,<br />
    I lay me down to rest.</p>
<p>If there be evil threat or quirk,<br />
Or covert act intent on me,<br />
God free me and encompass me,<br />
    And drive from me mine enemy.</p>
<p>In name of the Father precious,<br />
And of the Spirit of healing balm,<br />
In name of the Lord Jesus,<br />
    I lay me down to rest.<br />
*         *         *         *<br />
God, help me and encompass me,<br />
    From this hour till the hour of my death.</p></td>
